description: This is a cricket fact skill added to Alexa. When you ask Alexa about some interesting fact about cricket, it searched its facts list and randomly tells one of the fact about cricket which is a must know fact or very interesting fact of the cricket.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask cricket facts to give me interesting facts about cricket
Alexa, ask cricket facts to give me some information about cricket
name: Cricket Facts
shortDescription: This is a Cricket Fact skill used to tell some interesting facts about Cricket sports
